<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1915-05-03T12:55:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1915-05-02T05:00:00-05:00" n="548" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d548">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 300.115G95</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The Consul at Plymouth</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Stephens</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                </hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Plymouth</hi></placeName>, <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research" calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1915-05-03T12:55:00-05:00" notBefore="1915-05-02T10:00:00+00:00"><hi rend="italic">undated</hi></date>.<lb/>[<hi rend="italic">Received
                                        May 3, 1915, 12.55 p. m.</hi>]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>American tank steamer <hi rend="italic">Gulflight</hi> torpedoed of
                                Scilly 1st instant. Captain died heart failure, body landed. Two of
                                crew drowned, thirty-four saved. Vessel afloat, patrol boats
                                attempting tow her into Scilly.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stephens</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>